There are only two things that will arrest your temptation to call me out... fear and common sense!  Since you have no common sense, I strongly suspect that it is fear.  Especially, in view of the fact that you have always been a coward and an idiot, do I conclude that you are nothing but a noisey distraction.  The evidence of my contempt, presented here, is exactly what you need to file a libel and slander suit.  The problem, however, is that investigation and close scrutiny would document my allegations.  Futhermore, your postings here (in abundance) not only brand you as a weak man but also as one who is very sick.<br>
I propose that this person &quot;BACSI&quot; is just another creation of yours, a figment of your imagination, someone with whom you can carry on a sick dialogue.<br>
I am certain that Art and James, and others who know me personaly are enjoying a good laugh at your expense, over your impotent and foolish challenge.  If however, your stupidity overwhelms your fear.. I will reluctantly accept your challenge only if you press me in person.  If you chose that course of action.. don't bother to buy a round trip ticket.. it would be your final foolish act!<br>
My effort here is not to engage you but to alert others that you are a seriously deranged person... and not a spokesman for patriots.<br><br>
Get some help!<br><br>
